Home / Explore Products / Cabinetry Products








Cabinetry Products




						 
					

As one of the largest manufacturers of kitchen and bath cabinetry in the world, we offer approximately 300 styles in more than 20 lines. From custom-assembled cabinetry to ready-to-assemble kitchen and bath cabinets, we offer a wide range of products to fit your needs. Our unmatched selection of stylish, high-quality products are available at a variety of price levels. Our brands are favored by builders, dealers, distributors and home centers throughout North America and around the world.



Brands

DeNova
Kraftmaid
Merillat
Moores
QualityCabinets

 
 






	The DeNova® countertop collection includes natural granite, marble and quartz, as well as solid surface tops, in stock, semi-custom and custom configurations for bath, kitchen and beyond. Through its association with cabinet brands KraftMaid®, Merillat® and QualityCabinets™, DeNova® countertops provide a fully integrated countertop/cabinet solution that delivers beautifully coordinated design, and efficient, economical same-day countertop and cabinet installation.

Visit The Website


Customer Service:
1-866-277-9131





























 


























	KraftMaid® leads the semi-custom cabinetry industry with innovative product design, a robust collection of more than 100 trend-on door styles and more than 45 furniture-quality finishes. Based in Ann Arbor, Mich., and manufactured by Masco Cabinetry, KraftMaid brand cabinetry is backed by a limited lifetime warranty. 

Visit The Website


Customer Service:
1-888-562-7744









	Merillat® cabinets add meaningful innovation and functional storage to make prepping, cooking, entertaining and living in the kitchen easier. Merillat is based in Ann Arbor, Mich., and part of Masco Cabinetry. All Merillat products carry the seal of the Kitchen Cabinet Manufacturer Association (KCMA). A leader in environmental stewardship, Masco Cabinetry has been granted an Environmental Stewardship Program certificate by the KCMA and is ISO 14001 certified.

Visit The Website


Customer Service:
1-866-850-8557





























 


























	Moores® is committed to giving its customers the best possible value in terms of quality, service, delivery, product design and performance. Moores' product portfolio encompasses an extensive range of cabinets for the kitchen and bathroom. These are available in traditional, classical and contemporary designs as well as modern and continental styles.

Visit The Website


Customer Service:
Eagle - 1(800)640-5435 or Limerick - 1(800)282-7207









	Simple and affordable, QualityCabinets™ helps transform living spaces into spaces you’ll love, with cabinetry solutions that add long-lasting value and bring utility, comfort and beauty to a home. Based in Ann Arbor, Mich., and manufactured by Masco Cabinetry, QualityCabinets products are certified by the Kitchen Cabinet Manufacturers Association and exceed or meet industry standards for construction and performance.

