Plumbing Products




						 
					

We are a world leader in manufacturing plumbing products, with access to broad distribution channels worldwide. Through our premier brands, we are able to offer an array of styles and finishes to enhance your home. Our stylish, innovative products add convenience, enhance performance and improve your everyday experience with water. 



